246
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:31,380
Linda y yo vamos a salir
a cenar esta noche.

247
00:16:31,430 --> 00:16:34,390
Invitaremos a una chica
bien guapa e iremos todos.

248
00:16:34,430 --> 00:16:36,720
